// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/McffzM chiral combined cube composition, 2024 jt
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/lcfBzM random cuboid unit cube confined

// A random cuboid subdivided chirally into nine cuboids:
// A random core cuboid, two axial cuboids, two times three chiral cuboids.

// Some cuboids have been replaced by frames to show internal structure.

// Note that the chiral components always overlap.
// Treating the three back chiral components and the axis components as solid
// while treating the three front chiral components as empty space,
// there is always a spiral path from the bottom to the top of the structure
// which would be useful if the structure were to be used
// in level design for a computer game (imagine ladders up the walls).

// tags: cube, subdivision, composition, unit, combined, chiral

